      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REGAL SAINT (6) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 2.75 lengths at this track in a handy 19.78. Has a tricky draw to overcome but goes well over this trip. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Looks a key chance if runs up to latest figure. VERMENTINO (7) was the fastest winner on the program last time out, running away to score by one length (22.00) at this track. Should be in this for a long way. WEATHER MAN RICK (1) is boxed nicely on the inside. Last start finished 7th in a P5 on May 25 over 300m at Q Straight behind Hot Pink Double beaten 2.5 lengths (17.06). Among the main chances.",
